{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1275097, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 251471, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "刚刚的dz表示自己也经常超车，但我平均5s回头确认一次路况，从来没有别过别人（除了紧急避让），个人认为技术好不好都没关系，但技术不好还非要超车/随意变道真的是铁脑瘫", "timestamp": 1615956945, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1275198, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 251471, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "特别是突然左转弯的，真是…", "timestamp": 1615957844, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1275210, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 251471, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "确实", "timestamp": 1615957924, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1275213, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 251471, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一般左侧超车，嗖的一下就过去了", "timestamp": 1615957939, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1275222, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 251471, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一般特别快的时候会按铃", "timestamp": 1615958049, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1275327, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 251471, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "变道不回头看路4000+😅", "timestamp": 1615959332, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1275573, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 251471, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我爪巴，我就是那个疯狂提速的…感觉骑快一点有快感…不过仅限饭前且路上没人的时候", "timestamp": 1615961973, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 251471, "reply": 7, "tag": null, "text": "总感觉学校有些人骑车真的太莽了2333\n很多人好像根本意识不到岔路转弯的时候应该示意一下，这样就算不撞上也很容易逼停后面的车，真的难受。。\n好吧我也承认，我骑车快，经常超车。不过快不是那么夸张的快，就是比路上慢慢骑的车流快，超车也不会故意影响其他车的速度和路线。大家会反感这种吗？\n#251462", "timestamp": 1615956695, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1615961976, "url": "", "vote": {}}}